# Coverage floor per Go package.
# Format: <package-path> <minimum-percent>
# A 2pp slack vs current observed coverage absorbs run-to-run noise
# without letting silent regressions slip in. Bump thresholds upward
# whenever a package's real coverage rises so the floor tracks intent.

